A quick easy makeup which I usually wear when in a no foundation mood.😁

BB cream- @paeseindia 

Compact- @sephora_india mineral foundation compact

Mascara- @smashboxindia superfan

These are not your regular matte lipstick, the soft blur matte lipstick by @rufa_beauty have a very unique mousey, velvety texture that glides on smoothly giving a very beautiful soft# matte finish.🤩

After trying these lipsticks, I immediately messed their team telling how beautiful the shades and formula is😍

#kenny_patel__ #nudelipstick #rufabeauty #softblur #mattelips

I think anybody who doesn’t want the fuss of choosing what liner goes with what lipstick and what gloss to put on top, just get this lip kit you can do all kind of lip finishes.🤩

This lip kit by @blurindia has a lip liner, lip oil, and a matte liquid lipstick.💗

The kit shown is the perfect nude lip kit, but there are different variants available so you can choose the shade according to your preference.

1. Darker than my ex’s soul Lip liner- very creamy and smooth and the best is, it’s retractable

Also it’s not just a lip liner, you can also use it as an eye pencil.💄

2. It’s giving honey lip oil- I just loved this lip oil, it’s not greasy and has a very subtle shine. Makes the lip look so juicy. 🫦

3.call me daddy liquid lipstick- super matte, and transfer proof, very comfortable and the shade is sooo beautiful.💄
